Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}超越無人所及的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs37.5\pos(980,993.75)}ものがたり
